snippet.title: EpicMashups
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel guys 🍻 I hope you like my videos 🔥 My name is Martin and I'm creating funny mashups and edits combined with then and now videos. That's my unique style! I'm mostly into superhero movies or Disney and Nick tv shows. But not only that, once for a while I'm making tributes for favourite actors or other cool stuff just to keep my creativity coming. My goal is to be better and better in this and ultimately make something exceptionally beautiful 💖. I usually make 2 videos a month, I know that's not much, but it takes a lot of time to put this together, I don't wanna be a video factory as some channels are.
Few words about me, I cherish creativity, beauty, humor, excellence, I like good music, movies, art, beautiful women :D and everything else what I'm putting into my videos. If you have any issue with copyrights please contact me, I do everything in good faith and I'm sure we can resolve any problem. Also, please subscribe to make me happy 💙
